title: Taylor Swift and Ed Sheeran dominate American Music Award nominations
text:
Taylor Swift and Ed Sheeran dominate American Music Award nominations 9:12pm IST - 00:59 
Taylor Swift leads with six nominations for the 2015 American Music Awards   
It looks like there is going to be no Blank Space in Taylor Swifts awards collection, as she has been nominated for six American Music Awards. British singer Ed Sheeran and The Weekend came a close second, nominated in 5 categories each for the 2015 awards. They will all compete for the biggest prize - artist of the year - which will be left in the fateful hands of fans- as awards are decided on their votes. Meghan Trainor, Spectre soundtrack singer Sam Smith and American rapper Nicki Minaj have all been nominated for 3 awards each. Fans have until Nov 11th to vote for their favourite acts, with the ceremony being hosted by Jennifer Lopez in Los Angeles on Nov 22nd.  //in.reuters.com/video/2015/10/14/taylor-swift-and-ed-sheeran-dominate-ame?videoId=365940103&videoChannel=102
